# Build context is the repo root (compose `build.context: ..`).
# Keep heavy / environment-specific artifacts out of the image build.

# Dependencies (reinstalled in the builder stage)
**/node_modules

# Build outputs (regenerated by `pnpm -r build`)
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/.vite
*.tsbuildinfo

# Live, server-authoritative state — never bake into an image
data/state
**/state/session.json
**/state/session-log.md

# VCS + local env + misc
.git
.gitignore
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/*.log
.DS_Store
